{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/2017/07/31/Azure-Azure_Container_Instance_Overview/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Azure - Azure Container Instances 初體驗","date":"31 July 2017","author":"Sky Chang","excerpt":null,"tags":["Azure","Container","ACI","Docker","Linux"],"coverImage":null},"id":"a354268c-b3b4-5105-a67e-0832a4eabbaa","html":"<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>這段時間，連續的探討 ACS 的 Kubernetes，但其實這幾天，在 Azure 上的容器服務，又出現了一個更方便，更強大的容器服務，也就是今天的主題，Azure Container Instances ( ACI )。</p>\n<h2>關於 Azure Container Instances</h2>\n<p>大家回想一下，目前雲端上的服務，如果要使用容器，我們必須怎要做？以 Azure 來說，大概上有這幾種方法 ( 可能沒有全部列出 )，最經典的，就是建立一台 Windows Server 的 VM，或是 Linux VM 來支援容器，一個是簡單，便捷的 App Service，目前可以提供 Linux 上傳上去：其次就是我們最近連發的 ACS 主題，透過 Azure Container Service 來建立 Kubernetes 等，來支援 Container：但是如大家所知，無論是 VM，或是 ACS ，其實底層也是必須要搭配 VM 來搭建，而建立的過程中，可能也需要一點時間：但有的時候，我們會希望能和建立 VM 一樣的方便，甚至比 VM 建立的還要迅速。</p>\n<p>沒錯，這就是 Azure Container Instances 的由來，也是小弟一直很期待的一個服務。</p>\n<p>那 Azure Container Instances ( ACI ) 有什麼好處呢？根據<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-instances/container-instances-overview\">官網</a>的描述有幾項特點。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>超。快速啟動</li>\n<li>虛擬機層級的安全性</li>\n<li>想要多大多小，自型定義</li>\n<li>提供對外的 IP</li>\n<li>超方便的儲存體支援</li>\n<li>支援 Linux / Windows 容器</li>\n<li>輕鬆的群組與互相協調</li>\n</ul>\n<p>容器提供了虛擬機顯著啟動的好處。隨著Azure的容器實例，您可以在幾秒鐘內開始建置 Windows / Linux 容器，而無需部署和管理虛擬機；而也因為是虛擬層級的容器服務，所以可以說，每一台硬體就是提供給你 run 容器，所以，你可以輕易地調整你 run 這個容器的 cpu 大小和記憶體：當然，透過 Azure 整體的網路服務，在未來更可以輕易地整合 Azure 網路服務：既然有網路，那當然也會有儲存體，所以可以透過 Azure File 直接的共享：最後，不光是一個容器，你也可以輕易地建立 Group，甚至和 Kubernetes 串連。</p>\n<p>沒錯， ACI 的未來就是如此看好 :)</p>\n<p>接下來，就依據官網的<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-instances/container-instances-quickstart\">教學</a>實際走一次吧</p>\n<h2>使用 Shell 建立</h2>\n<p>這邊，我們可以使用 Azure Cloud Shell 建立 ( 如下圖 )，或是 Azure Cli 來建立，小弟這邊就使用 Azure Cli 來建立吧，但 Azure Cli 版本請大於 2.0.12 ，<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli\">版本更新</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/89066/01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"01\"\n        title=\"01\"\n        src=\"/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/78d47/01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/56d15/01.png 200w,\n/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/d9f49/01.png 400w,\n/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/78d47/01.png 800w,\n/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/64756/01.png 1200w,\n/static/df2f034604c0378374e13b2448445ddc/89066/01.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>版本須大於 2.0.12，可用底下指令查看版本</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az --version</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/54daf7292b0dc351a3f3bac5ccdbce51/663f3/02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"02\"\n        title=\"02\"\n        src=\"/static/54daf7292b0dc351a3f3bac5ccdbce51/663f3/02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/54daf7292b0dc351a3f3bac5ccdbce51/56d15/02.png 200w,\n/static/54daf7292b0dc351a3f3bac5ccdbce51/d9f49/02.png 400w,\n/static/54daf7292b0dc351a3f3bac5ccdbce51/663f3/02.png 650w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>建立資源群組</h2>\n<p>基本上，東西都是要放到資源群組裡面，所以我們就先建立一個稱為 ACITestGroup 且在東美的資源群組。\n（ 目前東亞不支援，此服務還在 Previrw )</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az group create --name ACITestGroup --location eastus</code></pre></div>\n<p>完成如下</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1db4e658e691cfc73539b4b1cf559b53/e5adc/03.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"03\"\n        title=\"03\"\n        src=\"/static/1db4e658e691cfc73539b4b1cf559b53/78d47/03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1db4e658e691cfc73539b4b1cf559b53/56d15/03.png 200w,\n/static/1db4e658e691cfc73539b4b1cf559b53/d9f49/03.png 400w,\n/static/1db4e658e691cfc73539b4b1cf559b53/78d47/03.png 800w,\n/static/1db4e658e691cfc73539b4b1cf559b53/e5adc/03.png 826w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>建立容器</h2>\n<p>接下來，我們就可以用指令快速建立一個 nginx 的容器，並且放到 ACITestGroup 的資源群組，且要公開 ip。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az container create --name nginx --image nginx --resource-group ACITestGroup  --ip-address public</code></pre></div>\n<p>完成後，我們就可以從下圖看到建立完成的相關資訊。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/d31ed/04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"04\"\n        title=\"04\"\n        src=\"/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/78d47/04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/56d15/04.png 200w,\n/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/d9f49/04.png 400w,\n/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/78d47/04.png 800w,\n/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/64756/04.png 1200w,\n/static/974cd2054f5da5be69be00ab23e47788/d31ed/04.png 1434w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>因為是對外 ip ，所以我們可以直接使用此 ip 瀏覽。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/89066/05.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"05\"\n        title=\"05\"\n        src=\"/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/78d47/05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/56d15/05.png 200w,\n/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/d9f49/05.png 400w,\n/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/78d47/05.png 800w,\n/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/64756/05.png 1200w,\n/static/93813c9da729cb27dbcc3fafa0400146/89066/05.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果，想查看所有的 container ，也可以用底下的指令。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az container list</code></pre></div>\n<p>或是針對其中一個 Container 查看。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az container show --name nginx  --resource-group ACITestGroup</code></pre></div>\n<p>當然，也可以從 Portal 的資源群組查看，只是目前 Portal 裡面是看不到 Public IP 的。( 等未來吧 )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/89066/06.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"06\"\n        title=\"06\"\n        src=\"/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/78d47/06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/56d15/06.png 200w,\n/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/d9f49/06.png 400w,\n/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/78d47/06.png 800w,\n/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/64756/06.png 1200w,\n/static/b9d1e58cc6278d3229fe7f0068571545/89066/06.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>查看容器 Log</h2>\n<p>如要查看 Log ，可以用底下指令</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az container logs --name nginx --resource-group ACITestGroup</code></pre></div>\n<p>結果如下圖。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3808a2bee832dacd70c5eccd0d5bb6e7/e5adc/07.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"07\"\n        title=\"07\"\n        src=\"/static/3808a2bee832dacd70c5eccd0d5bb6e7/78d47/07.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3808a2bee832dacd70c5eccd0d5bb6e7/56d15/07.png 200w,\n/static/3808a2bee832dacd70c5eccd0d5bb6e7/d9f49/07.png 400w,\n/static/3808a2bee832dacd70c5eccd0d5bb6e7/78d47/07.png 800w,\n/static/3808a2bee832dacd70c5eccd0d5bb6e7/e5adc/07.png 826w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>刪除容器</h2>\n<p>最後，如果要刪除，我們可以下底下指令。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">az container delete --name nginx --resource-group ACITestGroup</code></pre></div>\n<p>結果如下圖。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fd52dd4534d6cdd98ad2bab7e3d2f1ff/e5adc/08.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"08\"\n        title=\"08\"\n        src=\"/static/fd52dd4534d6cdd98ad2bab7e3d2f1ff/78d47/08.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd52dd4534d6cdd98ad2bab7e3d2f1ff/56d15/08.png 200w,\n/static/fd52dd4534d6cdd98ad2bab7e3d2f1ff/d9f49/08.png 400w,\n/static/fd52dd4534d6cdd98ad2bab7e3d2f1ff/78d47/08.png 800w,\n/static/fd52dd4534d6cdd98ad2bab7e3d2f1ff/e5adc/08.png 826w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>後記</h2>\n<p>這篇是照著官網，很簡單的一個初體驗，但從這次的體驗已經可以感受到，Azure 對於 Container 的發展，其實整整邁進了一大步，相信未來一定會有更多更好玩的服務出現！！</p>\n<h2>參考資料</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-instances/container-instances-overview\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-instances/container-instances-overview</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-instances/container-instances-quickstart\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-instances/container-instances-quickstart</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"前言 這段時間，連續的探討 ACS 的 Kubernetes，但其實這幾天，在 Azure 上的容器服務，又出現了一個更方便，更強大的容器服務，也就是今天的主題，Azure Container Instances ( ACI )。 關於 Azure Container…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Azure - Azure Container Service - Kubernetes 第一次的部署","tags":["Azure","Container","ACS","Kubernetes","Docker","Linux"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2017/07/30/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First_Create/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First_Create/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First_Create.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"VSTS - 解決 Git 無法同步之問題","tags":["Azure","VSTS","TFS","Git"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2017/09/09/VSTS-Resolve_Git_connection_failure/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/VSTS-Resolve_Git_connection_failure/VSTS-Resolve_Git_connection_failure.md"}}}}